Class ContentMigrationRecord

java.lang.Object
org.onehippo.forge.content.exim.core.ContentMigrationRecord
All Implemented Interfaces:

public class ContentMigrationRecord extends Object implements Serializable
Content Migration record which is used to keep execution information of a unit of content migration work item.
